data.description: Welcome to this incredible home on Kosciusko Street with views of the Mississippi and Arch! This updated 3 bedroom 3 bath home features tall ceilings, bright open rooms, exposed brick walls, a large entry foyer, and more! Main floor is bright and open with a bathroom, and a large kitchen with plenty of cabinets for storage, kitchen opens to a balcony and private patio, perfect for entertaining and relaxing! Den/Office off the kitchen. The master suite is large with plenty of closet space and an amazing master bath with double sinks, tub, and separate shower, opens to upper balcony. The spacious third floor features an additional bedroom and living space with open beams, skylights, and incredible views! Garage parking w bonus driveway for extra parking. A rare find!!! All this and in the perfect location, close to many restaurants, shops, Anheuser Busch Brewery, Soulard, Cherokee Street, and more! This incredibly well done home is a must see! Showings begin Saturday, April 20th at 9am!
